Title: How Market-AI Can Transform Recruitment Workflows — A Product Case Study

Intro
Hiring remains one of the most critical — and time-consuming — activities at fast-growing companies. Recruiters sift through noisy channels, hiring managers receive inconsistent shortlists, and teams lack real-time market signals like compensation and candidate availability. This case study explores how a "Market-AI" — an AI product that combines candidate discovery, explainable screening, and market intelligence — can change recruitment workflows to speed hiring and improve match quality.

